        YOU_WANT_TO_MAKE_IN_CASE_YOU_DIDN                                                  = 3124,  -- You want to make %? In case you didn't already know, a volatile objectaru like that needs to be kept in a special container.
        SUCH_A_CONTAINER_CAN_BE_SYNTHESIZED_IF_YOU                                         = 3125,  -- Such a container can be synthesized if you have two % and %. And if my memory serves me true, % serves as the bonding agentaru.
        I_HEAR_CAN_BE_HAD_WITHIN_THE_MAZE                                                  = 3126,  -- %, I hear, can be had within the Maze of Shakhrami. Not lying scattered about the floors, obviously. One of the crawlers there might be willing to partaru with one, but if not...well, you adventuring types know what to do.
        OH_DID_I_MENTION_NATURALLY_TO_SYNTHESIZE_YOU                                       = 3127,  -- Oh, did I mention %? Naturally, to synthesize %, you'll be needing one of those, too.
        YOU_WISH_TO_SYNTHESIZE_AH_YES_WELL_DO                                              = 3128,  -- You wish to synthesize %? Ah, yes. Well do I know that recipe! Its creation requires a few %.
        IN_TURN_MAKING_REQUIRES_AND_TOSS_INTO_THE                                          = 3129,  -- In turn, making % requires % and %. Toss % into the mix, and what you seek shall be yours.
        I_FEAR_WE_HAVEN_T_HERE_BUT_IT                                                      = 3130,  -- I fear we haven't % here. But it should please you to know that skeletons dwelling within the Gusgen Mines are known to drop one on occasion.
        WHAT_BRINGS_YOU_HERE_WELL_OF_ALL_THINGS                                            = 3131,  -- What brings you here? Well, %, of all things... You couldn't hope to make one without some %, but I fear they aren't often stocked by vendors.
        BUT_YOU_STRIKE_ME_AS_AN_INTREPID_TYPE                                              = 3132,  -- But you strike me as an intrepid type, so I'll share with you some knowledge to help you on your way. Head over to Ordelle's Caves. Hunt enough bats there, and you might just come into some %. That's the main ingredient required to make %.
        ALL_THAT_REMAINS_THEN_IS_TO_BIND_IT                                                = 3133,  -- All that remains, then, is to bind it with % using %. Good luck!
        YOU_YES_THE_DESCRIPTION_FITS_I_DARESAY_YOU                                         = 3134,  -- You... Yes, the description fits. I daresay, you're the one she sent, yes?
        CAN_I_COUNT_ON_YOU_TO_AID_MY                                                       = 3135,  -- Can I count on you to aid my investigation once more?
        AT_MY_CLIENT_S_BEHEST_I_HAVE_PROCURED                                              = 3136,  -- At my client's behest, I have procured the item you require. But alas, doing so drained far more of my time and resources than had been reckoned. As recompense for having exerted undue effort, I would ask a favor of you. Do as I say, and you may consider the item yours.
        DO_AS_HE_SAYS_YES_NO                                                               = 3137,  -- Do as he says? Yes. No.
        VERY_GOOD_I_KNEW_I_COULD_COUNT_ON                                                  = 3138,  -- Very good. I knew I could count on us being on the same page. Now then, without further ado, I shall explain the task to you. It truly is simple.
        YOU_ARE_TO_INVESTIGATE_A_NUMBER_OF_CREATURES                                       = 3139,  -- You are to investigate a number of creatures dwelling within the Sea Serpent Grotto in my stead.
        SHOULD_YOU_NOT_POSSESS_AND_I_CAN_FURNISH                                           = 3140,  -- Should you not possess % and %, I can furnish you with both for a nominal fee of 800 gil.
        USING_THE_WILL_TURN_INTO_A_VISUAL_RECORD                                           = 3141,  -- Using the % will turn % into %--a visual record of the subject's physical characteristics.
        I_M_CURRENTLY_INVESTIGATING_THE_THE_AND_THE                                        = 3142,  -- I'm currently investigating the %, the %, and the %.
        HM_IT_APPEARS_YOU_ARE_OVERBURDENED_SPEAK_WITH                                      = 3143,  -- Hm? It appears you are overburdened. Speak with me again after you've reorganized your belongings.
        THAT_IS_MOST_DISAPPOINTING_SHE_WOULD_NOT_BE                                        = 3144,  -- That is most disappointing... She would not be pleased to hear of this.
        AH_YES                                                                             = 3145,  -- Ah, yes...
        A_TRULY_MENACING_IMAGE_OF_THE_ALL_THAT                                             = 3146,  -- A truly menacing image of the %! All that remains, then, is one each of the % and the %.
        DO_YOU_REQUIRE_AND_I_CAN_PROVIDE_YOU                                               = 3147,  -- Do you require % and %? I can provide you with both for a nominal fee of 800 gil.
        BUY_FOR_800_GIL_YOU_HAVE_YES_PLEASE                                                = 3148,  -- Buy for 800 gil? (You have #) Yes, please. No, thank you.
        SHOULD_YOU_NOT_POSSESS_AND_I_CAN_FURNISH_2                                         = 3149,  -- Should you not possess % and %, I can furnish you with both for a nominal fee. I've recently depleted my stores, however, so you will have to wait until the next shipment arrives.
        IT_APPEARS_YOU_HAVEN_T_ENOUGH_GIL                                                  = 3150,  -- It appears you haven't enough gil.
        AH_A_POSITIVELY_IMPOSING_IMAGE_OF_THE_ALL                                          = 3151,  -- Ah, a positively imposing image of the %! All that remains, then, is one of the %.
        I_VE_EAGERLY_AWAITED_YOUR_RETURN_WITH_THIS                                         = 3152,  -- I've eagerly awaited your return. With this image of the %, I hold your task fulfilled.
        AS_PROMISED_I_RELINQUISH_THIS_TO_YOU_SHOULD                                        = 3153,  -- As promised, I relinquish this to you. Should another be required, you shall find me here.
        I_NEED_IMAGES_OF_THE_THE_AND_THE                                                   = 3154,  -- I need images of the %, the %, and the %.
