        I_D_BETTER_TELL_THE_OLD_WIFE_TOO                                                   = 3296,  -- I'd better tell the old wife too... Oh, but it's top secret, right? Then I'd better not, but...
        OH_SO_YOU_RE_A_FOREIGNER_HUH_THIS                                                  = 3297,  -- Oh, so you're a foreigner, huh? This is Windurst's Port District.
