        THANK_YOU_MASTER_BUT_OUR_LEAK_IS_IN                                                = 11528,  -- Thank you, Master, but our leak is in another Mog House! Bring this to me when we're back home in [San d'Oria/Bastok/Windurst], won't you, kupo?
