        BUT_ENOUGH_OF_THIS_CHITCHAT_IF_I_DON                                               = 13004,  -- But enough of this chitchat. If I don't catch somethin' for tonight's dinner, my wife'll clean me, gut me, and have me in a fryin' pan faster than you can say Galka meuniere!
