        THEY_PROVIDE_COURSES_ON_PRACTICAL_CHOCOBO_RIDING_AND                               = 13393,  -- They provide courses on practical chocobo riding and the proper ways to care for a chocobo, as well as working to improve the treatment of chocobos from here to Aht Urhgan.
