        STRENGTH_IS_A_TERM_USED_TO_DESCRIBE_THE                                            = 13400,  -- Strength is a term used to describe the chocobo's leg power. The more strength a chocobo has, the faster it will be able to run. Rental chocobos have been raised with an emphasis on this attribute.
