        NEXT_WE_HAVE_BEING_RIDDEN_BY                                                       = 15211,  -- Next we have [Pure Beauty/Ambitious Impact/Young Typhoon], being ridden by [the chocogirl next door, Hazina/dark chocostalker, Pikanza/self-proclaimed chocogeek, Qunbubu].
