        SAKURA_SAYS_THOUSANDS_OF_HOURS_OF_CHOCORESEARCH_HAVE                               = 15214,  -- Sakura says, Thousands of hours of chocoresearch have sharpened the mind of this jolly jockey into a pointy stick, ready to poke and prod anyone who dares stand in her way.
