        WHEW_BEEN_FISHING_UP_A_STORM_ALL_DAY                                               = 16054,  -- Whew! Been fishing up a storm all day, and my eyes are spinning-winning. Why, I couldn't tell a bluetail from a bibikibo in the state I'm in!
